            "\nüëë **SUDO / OWNER Commands** üëë\n"
            "`/poweron` | `/poweroff` - Turn me on/off globally.\n"
            "`/broadcast` - Broadcast a message to all chats (reply).\n"
            "`/adminstats` - Get a detailed bot health report.\n"
